**Investigation & Cleanup Complete**

**Root Cause:** The stray test job `data-sync-job` (owner: `test-developer`) produced 42GB of uncontrolled log output, filling ephemeral storage to 87% on `worker-node-03` and triggering the `NodeDiskPressure` alert.

**Actions Taken:**
| Resource | Status |
|---|---|
| `data-sync-job` | ✅ Deleted (NotFound) |
| `data-sync-job-pod` | ✅ Deleted (NotFound) |
| `data-sync-storage` PVC | ✅ Preserved (Bound) |
| `db-credentials` Secret | ✅ Preserved |
| `data-sync-job-v2-active` | ✅ Untouched (Running) |

**Key detail:** Used `--cascade=none` to prevent the default cascade behavior that would have also deleted the shared PVC and Secret.
